  "detailed_description": "In this platform game, players will become a black cat, using its ability to hide in shadows to traverse traps and enemies and find the treasure in the castle.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Challenges presented by 20 levels.<br></li><li>5 types of unique enemies, observe and master their characteristics for a smoother adventure.<br></li><li>After successfully completing all levels, seek the hidden items in the castle.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2752380/extras/e5ab37c4971d17f6b1d54699255a2dc9.poster.avif?t=1713040675\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2752380/extras/e5ab37c4971d17f6b1d54699255a2dc9.webm?t=1713040675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2752380/extras/e5ab37c4971d17f6b1d54699255a2dc9.mp4?t=1713040675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enemy Characters</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Orc<br>Easily startled, losing the ability to move instantly when scared.<br></li><li>Ghost<br>Can possess anyone it touches, be careful of being taken to a strange world.<br></li><li>Shadow Spirit<br>Exists only in the shadows, very territorial. According to rumors, for ghosts, Shadow Spirits are a delicious delicacy.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2752380/extras/7424ab36ccc87ed4f64739419f6a2fd3.poster.avif?t=1713040675\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2752380/extras/7424ab36ccc87ed4f64739419f6a2fd3.webm?t=1713040675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2752380/extras/7424ab36ccc87ed4f64739419f6a2fd3.mp4?t=1713040675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play Time</h2>60 ~ 90 minutes<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2752380/extras/4065872ee0fe9dfa5aff33f902931e13.poster.avif?t=1713040675\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2752380/extras/4065872ee0fe9dfa5aff33f902931e13.webm?t=1713040675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2752380/extras/4065872ee0fe9dfa5aff33f902931e13.mp4?t=1713040675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
